OL,3,C'It was not about money': Kincora
OL,4,Cvictim settles spy claim legal action
OL,6,FA victim of abuse at the notorious
OL,7,FKincora Boys' Home has obtained an
OL,8,Fundisclosed settlement over claims
OL,9,Fthat a paedophile housemaster was
OL,10,Fprotected from prosecution because of
OL,11,Fhis status as an MI5 agent.
OL,13,FGary Hoy had taken legal action
OL,14,Fagainst the PSNI and Home Secretary
OL,15,Fover claims the authorities enabled
OL,16,Fabuser William McGrath to target
OL,17,Fvulnerable victims.
