OL,3,C'It was not about money': Kincora
OL,4,Cvictim settles spy claim legal action
OL,6,FWith no admission of liability, the
OL,7,Fcase was resolved on confidential
OL,8,Fterms at the High Court in Belfast on
OL,9,FMonday 16 June.
OL,11,FThe 63-year-old declared afterwards:
OL,12,F"This case was never about the money,
OL,13,Fit was about holding them to account."
OL,15,FMr Hoy sought damages for the ordeal
OL,16,Fhe endured after being sent to the now
OL,17,Fdemolished children's home in east
OL,18,FBelfast during the 1970s.
