OL,3,C'It was not about money': Kincora
OL,4,Cvictim settles spy claim legal action
OL,6,FAt the centre of the action was the
OL,7,Frole played by senior member of staff
OL,8,FWilliam McGrath, who became known as
OL,9,Fthe 'Beast of Kincora'.
OL,11,FMcGrath was jailed in 1981 for abusing
OL,12,Fboys as part of a paedophile ring
OL,13,Foperated within the care facilities.
OL,15,FThe former housemaster, who died in
OL,16,Fthe early 1990s, also held a leading
OL,17,Fposition in the far-right loyalist
OL,18,Fmovement Tara.
