OL,6,FGary Hoy was not only abused by
OL,7,FMcGrath but other Kincora staff
OL,8,Fmembers Raymond Semple and Joseph
OL,9,FMains.
OL,11,FAll had been jailed but are all now
OL,12,Fdeceased.
OL,14,FLawyers for Mr Hoy claimed the
OL,15,Fauthorities enabled McGrath to target
OL,16,Fvulnerable young victims so that more
OL,17,Finformation about the grouping could
OL,18,Fbe obtained.
