OL,6,FThe alleged liability went as far as
OL,7,Factively obstructing RUC officers from
OL,8,Finvestigating and pursuing McGrath
OL,9,Fspecifically due to his role as an MI5
OL,10,Fagent, it was argued.
OL,12,FClaims for negligence and misfeasance
OL,13,Fin public office were advanced as part
OL,14,Fof wider actions against the PSNI,
OL,15,FHome Office and Department of Health.
OL,17,FThe defendants disputed responsibility
OL,18,Ffor any violation in the duty of care
OL,19,Fto those targeted at Kincora, which
OL,20,Fclosed in 1980 and was finally
OL,21,Fdemolished in 2022.
