OL,3,C'It was not about money': Kincora
OL,4,Cvictim settles spy claim legal action
OL,6,FA three-day trial was due to begin
OL,7,Ftoday, but counsel for Mr Hoy
OL,8,Fannounced that proceedings had been
OL,9,Fsettled on confidential terms.
OL,11,FNo further details were disclosed, and
OL,12,Fno admission of liability was made as
OL,13,Fpart of the resolution.
OL,15,FThe judge, Mr Justice Simpson,
OL,16,Fcommended the parties for reaching the
OL,17,Foutcome in a difficult case.
OL,19,FOutside court, Mr Hoy described the
OL,20,Fordeal he has endured for decades.
