OL,6,F"I have carried this burden since the
OL,7,Fage of 13; I never told anybody about
OL,8,Fit at the time, and I still have
OL,9,Fnightmares and flashbacks about the
OL,10,Fabuse," he said.
OL,12,FHis solicitor, Claire McKeegan of
OL,13,FPhoenix Law, described it as a huge
OL,14,Fday for all of the survivors of
OL,15,FKincora.
OL,17,F"No child should ever be subject to
OL,18,Fabuse while being in the care of the
OL,19,Fstate," she insisted.
